      • createResponse

        public static Response createResponse(@Nullable
                                      Request request,
                                      @Nullable
                                      String response,
                                      @Nullable
                                      String failedReason,
                                      @Nullable
                                      Message msg)
        Creates a new response.
        Parameters:
        request - the corresponding request to this response; sometimes can happen that it's not possible to find request and even so it's good to save response
        response - the response (response or failed reason must not be empty)
        failedReason - the failed reason (response or failed reason must not be empty)
        msg - the asynchronous message
        Returns:
        response entity
